1.title: 2017: Auditions 1
1.plot: Ant and Dec host the eleventh series of Britain's biggest talent competition as judges Simon Cowell, Amanda Holden, Alesha Dixon and David Walliams return for the sixth year running to give their verdicts on more weird and wonderful auditions. As the first round of auditions get under way, which performers will impress the judges and who will be going home disappointed? Only one talented act can claim victory, winning the opportunity to perform at this year's Royal Variety Performance.

2.title: 2017: Auditions 2
2.plot: The search for Britain's next best talent act, featuring singers, dancers, comedians, variety, and unusual talents of all kinds.

5.title: 2017: Auditions 5
5.plot: Ant and Dec host the UK's biggest talent show as it continues its eleventh series. The four formidable judges - Simon Cowell, Amanda Holden, Alesha Dixon and David Walliams - take their seats and offer their insights as they take in the fifth round of weird and wonderful auditions. Which acts will be returning for the semi-finals, taking a step closer to winning 250,000 pounds and the chance to show off their talents at this year's Royal Variety Performance?
